SG-SSB Ghana Appoints Hie as Managing Director, Graphic Reports

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-02-28T09:31:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/sg-ssb-ghana-appoints-hie-as-managing-director-graphic-reports.html
  SG-SSB Ltd ., a Ghanaian lender,
appointed Gilbert Hie as managing director, the  Daily Graphic 
reported.  Hie, who takes over from Alain Bellissard, was previously
chief executive officer of Bank Republic, a unit of  Societe
Generale  in  Georgia , the Accra-based newspaper said, citing a
company statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
 mdzawu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  